# 🌤 Weather App

A modern and responsive Weather Application built using **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript** that provides real-time weather information using the **OpenWeatherMap API**.

## 🌐 Live Demo

View the live project here:

[Live Demo](https://your-live-demo-link.com)

> Replace the above URL with your deployed GitHub Pages, Netlify, or Vercel link.

---

## 📌 Features

* 🔍 Search weather by city name
* 📍 Get weather using current location
* 🌡 Display current temperature
* ☁ Show weather conditions
* 💧 Display humidity percentage
* 🌬 Display wind speed
* 🖼 Dynamic weather icons
* 📱 Responsive user interface
* 🌄 Beautiful weather-themed background
* ⚡ Real-time weather updates using API

---

## 🛠 Technologies Used

* HTML5
* CSS3
* JavaScript (ES6)
* OpenWeatherMap API
* Geolocation API

